> "When is it? What is the advantage you get? You get… you get the following advantages. The… the good guys…"
> "Zephyr, because he's an assassin, gets an automatic critical."
> "So the question is, how do you guys want to try to surprise them? Do you want, like, splashing in the door is not a bad way to try to surprise somebody."

